Package com.itranswarp.jsonstream

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    JsonArrayFactory
    Called when a new JSON array is about to create.
    JsonObjectFactory
    Called when a new JSON object is created.
    JsonSerializable
    Object that implemented this interface will be serialize to JSON by itself.
    ObjectMapper
    Interface used to convert a JSON object Map<String, Object> to Java object.
    ObjectTypeFinder
    Return a subclass by detect subclass type from the parsed JSON map when instantiate an abstract class.
    TypeAdapter<T>
    Register a type adapter to convert between this type and string.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BeanObjectMapper
    Convert JSON object Map<String, Object> to JavaBean object, and recursively if necessary.
    JsonBuilder
    Builder for create JsonReader much easier.
    JsonReader
    Parse JSON as stream and return parsed object.
    JsonWriter  
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    JsonBindException
    Exception when bind JSON to JavaBean.
    JsonParseException
    Exception when parse JSON.
    JsonSerializeException
    Exception when serialize to JSON.
    ValidateException
    ValidateException represent a validation error.
